ens L</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2011-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/4FAB8667-E9B9-49E1-8A51-8B64D639380D"><gtr:id>4FAB8667-E9B9-49E1-8A51-8B64D639380D</gtr:id><gtr:title>Palaeoenvironmental change during the end-Guadalupian (Permian) mass extinction in Sichuan, China</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Palaeogeography, Palaeoclimatology, Palaeoecology</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/b962c7a353ca14b79718f5ef3e025f79"><gtr:id>b962c7a353ca14b79718f5ef3e025f79</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Lai X</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2008-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/A8B39EBD-3CE5-480A-AF60-3C2BF62B1592"><gtr:id>A8B39EBD-3CE5-480A-AF60-3C2BF62B1592</gtr:id><gtr:title>Volcanism, mass extinction, and carbon isotope fluctuations in the Middle Permian of China.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Science (New York, N.Y.)</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/09866cb960ff1211bed1bf62fcbe2795"><gtr:id>09866cb960ff1211bed1bf62fcbe2795</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Wignall PB</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2009-01-01</gtr:date><gtr:issn>0036-8075</gtr:issn></gtr:publication><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/3FBDB8E8-913B-4CB9-9D90-452CFDC9B42C"><gtr:id>3FBDB8E8-913B-4CB9-9D90-452CFDC9B42C</gtr:id><gtr:title>The mid-Capitanian (Middle Permian) mass extinction and carbon isotope record of South China</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>Palaeogeography, Palaeoclimatology, Palaeoecology</gtr:parentPublicationTitle><gtr:authors><gtr:author url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/person/fa0f9d6b5412fe8ef16a3caeb513b5d0"><gtr:id>fa0f9d6b5412fe8ef16a3caeb513b5d0</gtr:id><gtr:otherNames>Bond D</gtr:otherNames></gtr:author></gtr:authors><gtr:date>2010-01-01</gtr:date></gtr:publicati